# Drop-zone gitignore — track structure, not raw uploads.
# Raw PDFs / decks / screenshots stay on disk for the founder's reference
# but aren't pushed to remote (would bloat the repo, and the .md extraction
# is what carries the value).

# Ignore everything in this directory by default
*

# Except these tracked files:
!.gitignore
!README.md
!processed/

# Inside processed/, also ignore raw uploads — only keep the placeholder
processed/*
!processed/.gitkeep
